graph LR
    DSPO[Data Science Pipelines Operator]

    %% External Platform Dependencies
    DSPO -->|platform services| OpenShift[OpenShift 4.11+]
    DSPO -->|workflow engine| ArgoWorkflows[Argo Workflows]
    DSPO -->|legacy workflow engine| Tekton[Tekton Pipelines 1.8+]
    DSPO -.->|metrics collection| Prometheus[Prometheus Operator]
    DSPO -.->|TLS certificates| ServiceCA[service-ca / cert-manager]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    DSPO -->|deployed by| ODHOperator[opendatahub-operator]
    ODHDashboard[ODH Dashboard] -->|displays runs| DSPO
    ODHNotebooks[ODH Notebook Controller] -->|submits pipelines| DSPO

    %% Runtime Dependencies (within DSPA instances)
    subgraph DSPA_Runtime["DSPA Instance Runtime Dependencies"]
        direction TB
        API[API Server]
        WFC[Workflow Controller]
        PA[Persistence Agent]
        SWF[Scheduled Workflow]

        API -->|stores metadata| DB[(Database)]
        API -->|stores artifacts| Storage[(Object Storage)]
        PA -->|syncs state| API
        SWF -->|creates workflows| WFC
        WFC -->|executes| WorkflowPods[Workflow Pods]
        WorkflowPods -->|logs lineage| MLMD[ML Metadata]
    end

    DSPO -->|deploys| DSPA_Runtime

    %% External Services (Egress)
    DSPO -->|image pulls| Registry[Image Registry<br/>Quay.io / registry.redhat.io]
    API -.->|alternative storage| ExternalS3[External S3<br/>AWS / MinIO]
    API -.->|alternative database| ExternalDB[External Database<br/>MySQL / PostgreSQL]
    WorkflowPods -.->|artifact storage| ExternalS3

    %% Kubernetes API
    DSPO -->|resource management| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API]
    WFC -->|pod lifecycle| K8sAPI
    PA -->|watch workflows| K8sAPI

    %% Integration Points
    subgraph Integrations["Integration Points"]
        direction LR
        KFP_SDK[kfp SDK v2.x]
        Dashboard_UI[ODH Dashboard UI]
        CLI[kubectl / oc]
    end

    KFP_SDK -->|submits pipelines| API
    Dashboard_UI -->|queries| API
    CLI -->|creates| DSPA_CR[DataSciencePipelinesApplication CR]
    DSPA_CR -->|watched by| DSPO

    %% Styling
    style DSPO fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px,color:#fff

    style OpenShift fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ArgoWorkflows fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Tekton fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Prometheus fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ServiceCA fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style K8sAPI fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Registry fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px

    style ODHOperator fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ODHDashboard fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ODHNotebooks fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px

    style ExternalS3 fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ExternalDB fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px

    style DSPA_CR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px

    style API fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px,color:#fff
    style WFC fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px,color:#fff
    style PA fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px,color:#fff
    style SWF fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px,color:#fff
    style WorkflowPods fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px,color:#fff
    style DB fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px
    style Storage fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px
    style MLMD fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px

    style KFP_SDK fill:#dae8fc,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px
    style Dashboard_UI fill:#dae8fc,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px
